name: Awakening - Cover Collab x BA$H
description:
Awakening - Cover Collab x BA$H
Opened up my eyes new day, new awakening,
Read from the script and I had to get a prayer in,
Because life, Got me swimming in the shallow end,
The water’s getting deep and I ain’t trying to get swallowed in,
Uh, you know I got to stay focused, 
God is the motive and I’m swimming in the ocean,
Fighting with the sharks like a thief in the night,
Like I’m fighting through the dark, trying to spread the light.

Reading 1 Corinthians, Reading the scripts,
Reading of the King Again, He was sent, Let’s Repent,
Lord Heal me - When I die, No fiery pits,
Kingdom of your heaven, Yes I want to be on your list, list. X2

Moment of awake-ness, seeking through the pages,
Love is my arrangement, preaching through the music,
Holy Conversation, One ring, One Knee, Soul integration,
Sometimes I think back, eyes closed, snap back to reality, Satan is like a cavity,
Deceiving is his masterpiece, Remove his art inside of me,
Conviction leads it out of me, this is my awakening.

Reading 1 Corinthians, Reading the scripts,
Reading of the King Again, He was sent, Let’s Repent,
Lord Hear me - when I die, No fiery pits,
Kingdom of your heaven, Yes I want to be on your list, list. X2
